## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-102">當系統已經叫用強制回應對話方塊時，某些裝載設計工具的應用程式必須收到通知。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-102">Some applications that host designers need to be notified when a modal dialog box has been invoked.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-103">Visual Studio 就是這類主應用程式的範例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-103">Visual Studio is an example of such a host.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-104"><xref:System.Activities.Presentation.IModalService> 介面會提供可傳達目前強制回應狀態的介面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-104">The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.IModalService> interface provides an interface to communicate the current modal status.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-105">Windows 工作流程設計工具會呼叫 <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.IModalService.SetModalState%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-105">The Windows Workflow Designer calls the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.IModalService.SetModalState%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-106">當`isModal`參數設定為`true`，主機會收到通知，會顯示強制回應對話方塊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-106">When the `isModal` parameter is set to `true`, the host is notified that a modal dialog is displayed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-107">這是一項選擇性服務。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-107">This is an optional service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-108">如果主應用程式並不關心強制回應狀態，您就不需要使用此服務。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-108">If a host application does not care about the modal status,  you need not use the service.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-109">在目前的實作，會叫用的 Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) 訊息方塊 （這是強制回應對話方塊），如果<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.IModalService.SetModalState%2A>則不會呼叫。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-109">In the current implementation, if a Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF) message box (which is a modal dialog) is invoked, the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.IModalService.SetModalState%2A> is not called.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c27e5-110">如果主應用程式需要這項資訊，您就必須建立另一個解決方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c27e5-110">If the host application requires this information, another workaround must be created.</span></span>  
  
